1. First time setup:

echo "source /opt/ros/indigo/setup.bash" >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

cd <repo>
catkin_make
echo "source $(pwd)/devel/setup.bash" >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

2. Compile Code:
cd <repo>
catkin_make 

3. To Start Simulator & Rviz
cd <repo>
roslaunch robot_and_map.launch

4. Sample code which generates a path and publish is at <repo>/src/path_planner/path_generator.py
To run sample path generator:

rosrun path_planner path_generator.py

